parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dual pane window seal can cause fogging or clouding between the panes of glass, impairing the driver's visibility and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Fogging or clouding between the panes of glass
difficulty seeing out of windows
impaired visibility
glare or reflection/mirroring distortion
obstruction of view when using side mirrors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake caliper can cause the brake pedal to fall to the floor, leading to a loss of braking ability, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal falls to the floor
the brakes lock up without warning
the brakes exhibit resistance to braking pressures
the vehicle pulls to one side while braking
the brake system fails to function properly
the ABS malfunction light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadvertent brake application can cause excessive heat and damage to front brake parts, leading to a loss of braking ability, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brakes exhibit resistance to braking pressures
the vehicle pulls to one side while braking
the brake system fails to function properly
the ABS malfunction light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause the brakes to lock up, leading to a loss of control and increased stopping distance, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The ABS malfunction light is illuminated
the brakes lock up without warning
the vehicle pulls to one side while braking
the brake system fails to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Norcold refrigerator can cause food spoilage, discomfort, and inconvenience to the occupants, especially during extended trips or in hot weather conditions.
symptoms: The refrigerator stops cooling
refrigerant leaks out
the refrigerator is not functioning properly
food is spoiled due to inadequate cooling.
